The processing of this immense stream of information enables businesses to use and provide different products in different ways.
The most common uses focus on repair and maintenance, but depending on the country, there are also tools for managing spare parts or for calculating the sales or residual value of the car.
The only company that has a guide that informs about the value of used vehicles in Spain is Eurotax.
Audatex does not offer them in our country, but in the United States they do.
Taking into account the products offered by Audatex, it is easy to get support that can be used by professionals in the sector.
